1
00:00:51,030 --> 00:00:53,100
Vice Director Shen, the Director invites you.

2
00:00:53,100 --> 00:00:54,930
Please return to the tower with us.

3
00:00:54,930 --> 00:00:56,200
Minister Qin's men,

4
00:00:56,300 --> 00:00:58,160
but using the Director's banner.

5
00:00:59,830 --> 00:01:00,830
Interesting.

6
00:01:15,800 --> 00:01:16,630
Third Prince.

7
00:01:16,800 --> 00:01:18,930
The men have already been dispatched.

8
00:01:21,000 --> 00:01:21,460
My Lord.

9
00:01:21,730 --> 00:01:22,830
You're finally here.

10
00:01:22,830 --> 00:01:23,600
Young Master Shen.

11
00:01:23,600 --> 00:01:24,660
The person has been brought here.

12
00:01:24,660 --> 00:01:26,800
I've also sent someone to escort Miss Xiaocui back to her hometown to rest.

13
00:01:26,800 --> 00:01:27,730
Registrar Shen.

14
00:01:27,860 --> 00:01:29,920
Thanks to this heroine for saving us.

15
00:01:34,460 --> 00:01:36,720
The holy water sample from Ci'en Temple.

16
00:01:37,000 --> 00:01:38,460
Live insect eggs.

17
00:01:42,600 --> 00:01:44,759
My Lord, there was noise outside just now.

18
00:01:44,759 --> 00:01:46,820
I'm worried someone is following us.

19
00:01:49,930 --> 00:01:51,130
The medicine man is dealt with,

20
00:01:51,130 --> 00:01:52,930
but we shouldn't stay here long.

21
00:01:56,130 --> 00:01:58,430
This is a Soul-Devouring Gu egg.

22
00:01:58,900 --> 00:02:02,700
It was drawn in an ancient Western Regions book in my father's study.

23
00:02:14,300 --> 00:02:16,060
The Gu worm was activated remotely.

24
00:02:16,060 --> 00:02:17,920
Someone is trying to control him.

25
00:02:23,130 --> 00:02:25,200
The suppression method my father developed

26
00:02:25,200 --> 00:02:28,530
is to use silver needles on the Quchi, Chize, and Shaohai acupoints.

27
00:02:28,530 --> 00:02:31,400
This can temporarily sever the connection between the Gu worm and the control center.

28
00:02:31,400 --> 00:02:33,800
But the effect only lasts for twelve shichen.

29
00:02:33,800 --> 00:02:38,760
Just now, a voice in my head ordered me to kill you.

30
00:02:40,730 --> 00:02:41,900
The remote activation

31
00:02:41,900 --> 00:02:44,260
means the controller of the mother Gu knows we are here.

32
00:02:44,260 --> 00:02:46,329
There might be watchers outside the temple.

33
00:02:46,329 --> 00:02:47,230
Hoofbeats.

34
00:02:47,560 --> 00:02:48,329
Northwest.

35
00:02:48,660 --> 00:02:49,500
At least twenty riders.

36
00:02:49,500 --> 00:02:50,430
Half a mile away.

37
00:02:54,329 --> 00:02:56,400
Standard light armor of the Imperial City Bureau.

38
00:02:56,400 --> 00:02:57,800
They brought ballistas.

39
00:02:57,930 --> 00:02:59,329
How long can acupuncture suppress it?

40
00:02:59,329 --> 00:03:00,260
Twelve shichen.

41
00:03:00,360 --> 00:03:01,700
But if the mother Gu keeps applying pressure,

42
00:03:01,700 --> 00:03:03,000
the suppression time will shorten.

43
00:03:03,000 --> 00:03:04,530
Unless we find the mother Gu

44
00:03:04,530 --> 00:03:06,060
and completely destroy it.

45
00:03:16,630 --> 00:03:17,460
My Lord.

46
00:03:17,460 --> 00:03:18,930
I have investigated secretly for three months.

47
00:03:18,930 --> 00:03:20,100
I found that besides Ci'en Temple

48
00:03:20,100 --> 00:03:21,560
and the Directorate of Astronomy's Black Tower,

49
00:03:21,560 --> 00:03:22,630
there are five other suspected

50
00:03:22,630 --> 00:03:23,660
soul power collection points:

51
00:03:23,660 --> 00:03:24,760
the ruins of Baiyun Temple in the east,

52
00:03:24,760 --> 00:03:25,660
the charity graveyard in the north suburbs,

53
00:03:25,660 --> 00:03:26,730
the foreign merchant warehouse in the West Market,

54
00:03:26,730 --> 00:03:27,960
and the backyard of the rouge shop in the south.

55
00:03:27,960 --> 00:03:28,890
Their locations

56
00:03:29,100 --> 00:03:30,630
all ultimately point to this Laojun Temple.

57
00:03:30,630 --> 00:03:31,960
Laojun Temple is a node.

58
00:03:32,000 --> 00:03:32,660
The medicine man was dealt with,

59
00:03:32,660 --> 00:03:34,030
and the Imperial City Bureau accurately surrounded the temple.

60
00:03:34,030 --> 00:03:34,630
This means this place

61
00:03:34,630 --> 00:03:36,030
was already under their surveillance.

62
00:03:36,030 --> 00:03:36,960
My Lord, you mean

63
00:03:37,000 --> 00:03:39,260
there's something fishy in this temple?

64
00:03:41,300 --> 00:03:42,560
The temple has been dilapidated for years.

65
00:03:42,560 --> 00:03:44,160
But the base of the statue is dust-free,

66
00:03:44,160 --> 00:03:45,800
and the stele's surface is abnormally worn.

67
00:03:45,800 --> 00:03:48,400
Someone must come here often.

68
00:03:58,230 --> 00:03:59,500
This cloud pattern

69
00:03:59,800 --> 00:04:01,530
is my father's private seal design.

70
00:04:01,530 --> 00:04:02,660
In his youth, he supervised the construction

71
00:04:02,660 --> 00:04:05,730
of the mechanisms and locks for the imperial mausoleum's underground palace.

72
00:04:05,730 --> 00:04:07,790
They are going to break the door down.

73
00:04:18,600 --> 00:04:20,959
Vice Director Shen is in a good mood.

74
00:04:21,630 --> 00:04:23,900
Having a secret rendezvous with rebels late at night,

75
00:04:23,900 --> 00:04:25,030
caught red-handed.

76
00:04:27,930 --> 00:04:29,060
Take them down!
